  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and <strong>1 SP</strong> to release a shout of your choice listed below.</p><p>Until the start of your next turn, you and creatures of your choice within 5 Spaces that can see or hear you are subjected to the effects of your shout.</p><p>A creature can only benefit from the same type of shout once at a time.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Fortitude Shout:</strong> Each creature gains Resistance (1) against the next source of Physical or Elemental damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Fury Shout:</strong> Each creature deals +1 damage on their next Attack against 1 target.</p></li><li><p><strong>Urgent Shout:</strong> Each creature gains +1 Speed until the start of your next turn.</p></li></ul>",
